title: Halloween Ends: The Complete Michael Myers Timeline

media:group.media:title: Halloween Ends: The Complete Michael Myers Timeline
media:group.media:description:
With the cinema release of Halloween Ends film, I thought now would be the best time to do the timeline of the Boogeyman, Michael Myers.
In this video we'll be going over the life, evolution and dark history of Michael Myers. Created by John Carpenter and Debra Hill, starring Jamie Lee Curtis. I review the events of Hallowen 1978, Halloween 2018, Halloween Kills (2021), as well as including a Halloween Ends (2022) analysis. So let's smash some pumpkins!

Thank you to @CZsWorld. Watch his Halloween playlist here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLL3r8G2ymJ00RCbiBf-lc3oddk09OgH8D

Music by: Karl Casey. White Bat Audio
